{"tid":2236335,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來香港仲有死刑！班走狗憑乜判人死刑？","createTime":"2020-10-09T11:27:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T14:01:08.000Z","uid":277640,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a4b800f51fc36ef90625dbd7edb4f99c73eb77cf","tid":2236335,"uid":277640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T11:27:44.000Z","msg":"香港需要大家繼續關注，希望大家唔好放棄香港。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港共搞老師，搞傳媒，搞法官。仆街港共死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地如果唔關注呢個老師，以後將會更多老師被清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">好簡單，click入下面條link, 花2分鐘填少少資料，一人一信要求撤回取消教師註冊決定。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【⚠️《要求教育局撤回取消教師註冊決定》一人一信行動📩】<br />\n<br />\n╭──────────────────╮<br />\n╞📧立即去信：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/email4teacher\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Femail4teacher&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzuDrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=3ed4ef4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/email4teacher</a><br />\n╰──────────────────╯<br />\n<br />\n早前一名九龍塘宣道小學教師製作關於言論自由的教案時，加入播放講述「民族黨」的鏗鏘集，而被教育局宣佈取消其教師註冊。但教學內容並無如局方所言「散播港獨訊息」，只是使用客觀新聞材料讓學生歸納分析，並沒有偏離言論自由的主題。加上言論自由作為普世價值，亦是《基本法》所保障的基本人權，無疑值得學習與討論。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"violet\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">九龍塘宣道小學亦曾兩度調查有關事件，均認為投訴不成立，教育局卻拒絕接納，</span></strong></span>甚至出譴責信予校長及副校長等六名教師，批評其監管不力、專業失德。我們認為是次事件<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">是一次對老師的政治打壓及對學校自主的侵犯，</span></strong></span>目的是在教師及學校之間製造白色恐怖，要教師自我審查，不敢再教育學生普世價值。<br />\n<br />\n因此，教育野聯同 進步教師同盟 Progressive Teachers' Alliance、 香港教育同行陣線 、 香港人教育支援平台 Hongkongers Education Support 發起一人一信行動，以群眾的力量去信手握教師註冊生殺大權的教育局常任秘書長李美嫦及教育局局長楊潤雄，要求教育局撤回取消教師註冊決定。在填Form後，Email內容會自動Send至教育局局長楊潤雄，以及教育局常任秘書長李美嫦的Email。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">守護教育，與教師學生同行，是每一位香港人的共同責任。</span></strong></span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n教育在野&middot;拒絕馴服<br />\n🖥 Facebook： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/edu_FB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fedu_FB&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzuDrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=8871a709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/edu_FB</a><br />\n📷Instagram： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/edu_IG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fedu_IG&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzuDrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=8701a5ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/edu_IG</a><br />\n📲Telegram： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/edu_TG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fedu_TG&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzuDrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=aae5b96b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/edu_TG</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xJpnCzO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxJpnCzO.jpg&h=cd0ff745&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8307cc6efd559ec939709371dc2e3e956ff1701b","tid":2236335,"uid":277640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T11:27:55.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9859839e857e8de21a28cf1ee4709a41b5fe7ac3","tid":2236335,"uid":277640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T11:28:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a9a3f201812beee59feb07f0adfb323e49f823","tid":2236335,"uid":277640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T11:28:23.000Z","msg":"做任務"},{"pid":"bcbe7efab369fa1c18d5f7f93a1475a0f8235c6f","tid":2236335,"uid":277640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T11:28:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c33ca68adbdc50390bb5eff9db86316fa61d96a","tid":2236335,"uid":277640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T11:28:49.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"d912c1914501d9d3990d4253108722984